===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|abycgan|ābycgan|lang=ang}} (corresponding to ''[[a-]]'' + ''[[buy]]''), from {{proto|Germanic|lang=en}}. Cognate with Gothic {{term|𐌿𐍃𐌱𐌿𐌲𐌾𐌰𐌽|tr=usbugjan|lang=got|sc=Goth}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/əˈbaɪ/}}
